There doesn&#39;t appear to be much to it. He uses a compass inside a box as the
indicator for possible paranormal events and has electronics to detect when
the compass needle moves. He also has an IR sensor and it&#39;s not clear to me
if it just senses changes in an IR field or if it uses IR to detect if the
compas needle moved.

There&#39;s no audio involved in it. My guess is that my Trifield meter does the
same thing basically but costs more and is less subject to false
triggerings.

Zack

